  17 Mar 2007; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> audtty-0.1.5a.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 169823

  09 Mar 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audtty-0.1.5a.ebuild:
  Mark stable on X86 for bug #169823.

